function vis_describeLocal {
    cat  << _EOF_
    Tree Traversal Facilities

Inputs: 
          leavesList, leavesOrdered, leavesExcludes
          nodesList, nodesOrdered, nodesExcludes

Outputs: 
          leavesEffective
          nodesEffective

A 'dir' is either a leaf or a node or ignorable as in (treeItemEnum)
_EOF_
}


