*  [[elisp:(org-cycle)][| ]]  [[elisp:(blee:ppmm:org-mode-toggle)][Nat]] [[elisp:(beginning-of-buffer)][Top]] [[elisp:(delete-other-windows)][(1)]] || IIF       ::  vis_bxtThereTag    [[elisp:(org-cycle)][| ]]
